      </Row>
      <Row ss:StyleID="Todo">
        <Cell><Data ss:Type="String">CORE</Data></Cell>
        <Cell><Data ss:Type="String">C7</Data></Cell>
        <Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Service CRM: Ticketing/Case Management</Data></Cell>
        <Cell><Data ss:Type="String">C7-S2</Data></Cell>
        <Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Sebagai support lead, saya bisa melihat queue dan SLA breach.</Data></Cell>
        <Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Ada endpoint queue + filter; dashboard menampilkan metrik SLA dasar dan backlog per assignee.</Data></Cell>
        <Cell><Data ss:Type="String">C7-S1</Data></Cell>
        <Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Could Have</Data></Cell>
        <Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Sales:Backlog; Support:S3</Data></Cell>
        <Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Todo</Data></Cell>
      </Row>

      <Row ss:StyleID="Todo">
        <Cell><Data ss:Type="String">PLUGIN</Data></Cell>
        <Cell><Data ss:Type="String">P1</Data></Cell>
        <Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Lead Assignment Rules</Data></Cell>
        <Cell><Data ss:Type="String">P1-S1</Data></Cell>
        <Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Sebagai admin, saya bisa set aturan assignment lead (round-robin/berdasarkan region/source).</Data></Cell>
        <Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Plugin menyimpan rules di config; perubahan tidak butuh deploy core. Ada validasi rule dan tombol test (simulate) pada sample lead.</Data></Cell>
        <Cell><Data ss:Type="String">C6-S1 (event lead.created), C6-S3 (config), C6-S2 bila butuh endpoint plugin</Data></Cell>
        <Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Must Have</Data></Cell>
        <Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Sales:S1; Support:Backlog</Data></Cell>
        <Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Todo</Data></Cell>
      </Row>
      <Row ss:StyleID="Todo">
        <Cell><Data ss:Type="String">PLUGIN</Data></Cell>
        <Cell><Data ss:Type="String">P1</Data></Cell>
        <Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Lead Assignment Rules</Data></Cell>
        <Cell><Data ss:Type="String">P1-S2</Data></Cell>
        <Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Sebagai sistem, saat lead dibuat, owner otomatis ditentukan oleh rule.</Data></Cell>
        <Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Pada event lead.created, plugin menentukan owner dan update lead. Audit log mencatat perubahan. Jika tidak match, fallback ke creator.</Data></Cell>
        <Cell><Data ss:Type="String">P1-S1, C6-S1</Data></Cell>
        <Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Must Have</Data></Cell>
        <Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Sales:S1; Support:Backlog</Data></Cell>
        <Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Todo</Data></Cell>
      </Row>

      <Row ss:StyleID="Todo">
        <Cell><Data ss:Type="String">PLUGIN</Data></Cell>
        <Cell><Data ss:Type="String">P2</Data></Cell>
        <Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Lead Scoring Rules</Data></Cell>
        <Cell><Data ss:Type="String">P2-S1</Data></Cell>
        <Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Sebagai sales ops, saya bisa mendefinisikan scoring rule berbasis atribut lead.</Data></Cell>
        <Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Rule bisa diaktif/nonaktif. Plugin menyediakan evaluasi otomatis (lead.created/updated) dan manual (run scoring) serta menyimpan hasil score.</Data></Cell>
        <Cell><Data ss:Type="String">C6-S1, C6-S3, C1 (opsional untuk custom score fields)</Data></Cell>
        <Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Should Have</Data></Cell>
        <Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Sales:S2; Support:Backlog</Data></Cell>
        <Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Todo</Data></Cell>
      </Row>
      <Row ss:StyleID="Todo">
        <Cell><Data ss:Type="String">PLUGIN</Data></Cell>
        <Cell><Data ss:Type="String">P2</Data></Cell>
        <Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Lead Scoring Rules</Data></Cell>
        <Cell><Data ss:Type="String">P2-S2</Data></Cell>
        <Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Sebagai user, saya bisa melihat score dan alasan (explain) ringkas.</Data></Cell>
        <Cell><Data ss:Type="String">UI menampilkan score + ringkasan rule yang applied. Breakdown sensitif bisa dibatasi role.</Data></Cell>
        <Cell><Data ss:Type="String">C6-S4 (UI slot) atau perubahan UI core lead detail</Data></Cell>
        <Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Could Have</Data></Cell>
        <Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Sales:Backlog; Support:Backlog</Data></Cell>
        <Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Todo</Data></Cell>
      </Row>

      <Row ss:StyleID="Todo">
        <Cell><Data ss:Type="String">PLUGIN</Data></Cell>
        <Cell><Data ss:Type="String">P3</Data></Cell>
        <Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Reminder &amp; Notification Automation</Data></Cell>
        <Cell><Data ss:Type="String">P3-S1</Data></Cell>
        <Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Sebagai user, saya bisa membuat rule reminder (mis. opportunity stage X &gt; 7 hari tanpa activity).</Data></Cell>
        <Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Rule bisa diaktif/nonaktif. Eksekusi event-driven atau scheduled. Ada dedupe agar tidak spam (per entity per periode).</Data></Cell>
        <Cell><Data ss:Type="String">C6-S1, notifications module sudah ada</Data></Cell>
        <Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Should Have</Data></Cell>
        <Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Sales:Backlog; Support:S1</Data></Cell>
        <Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Todo</Data></Cell>
      </Row>

      <Row ss:StyleID="Todo">
        <Cell><Data ss:Type="String">PLUGIN</Data></Cell>
        <Cell><Data ss:Type="String">P4</Data></Cell>
        <Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Email &amp; Calendar Sync (Logging ke Timeline)</Data></Cell>
        <Cell><Data ss:Type="String">P4-S1</Data></Cell>
        <Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Sebagai admin, saya bisa menghubungkan provider (Google/M365) untuk sync email/calendar (ingest).</Data></Cell>
        <Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Token disimpan sebagai secret plugin; koneksi bisa di-test dan di-disable; ada retry/backoff untuk error provider.</Data></Cell>
        <Cell><Data ss:Type="String">C6-S3 (secrets), C6-S2 (endpoint/webhook), C6-S1 (events optional)</Data></Cell>
        <Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Could Have</Data></Cell>
        <Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Sales:Backlog; Support:Backlog</Data></Cell>
        <Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Todo</Data></Cell>
      </Row>
      <Row ss:StyleID="Todo">
        <Cell><Data ss:Type="String">PLUGIN</Data></Cell>
        <Cell><Data ss:Type="String">P4</Data></Cell>
        <Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Email &amp; Calendar Sync (Logging ke Timeline)</Data></Cell>
        <Cell><Data ss:Type="String">P4-S2</Data></Cell>
        <Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Sebagai sistem, email/meeting relevan di-log ke timeline entity berdasarkan email contact/lead.</Data></Cell>
        <Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Sync membuat activity/note yang terhubung ke entity yang cocok; tidak membuat duplikat untuk message/event yang sama.</Data></Cell>
        <Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Timeline/notes/activities sudah ada; butuh matching strategy</Data></Cell>
        <Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Could Have</Data></Cell>
        <Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Sales:Backlog; Support:Backlog</Data></Cell>
        <Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Todo</Data></Cell>
      </Row>

      <Row ss:StyleID="Todo">
        <Cell><Data ss:Type="String">PLUGIN</Data></Cell>
        <Cell><Data ss:Type="String">P5</Data></Cell>
        <Cell><Data ss:Type="String">WhatsApp / Messaging Integration</Data></Cell>
        <Cell><Data ss:Type="String">P5-S1</Data></Cell>
        <Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Sebagai user, saya bisa menjalankan action “Send WhatsApp” dari contact/lead/opportunity.</Data></Cell>
        <Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Action hanya tampil jika plugin aktif. Aksi tercatat sebagai activity log dan punya throttling dasar.</Data></Cell>
        <Cell><Data ss:Type="String">C6-S4 (action slot), C6-S3 (secrets) bila pakai API provider</Data></Cell>
        <Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Could Have</Data></Cell>
        <Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Sales:Backlog; Support:Backlog</Data></Cell>
        <Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Todo</Data></Cell>
      </Row>
      <Row ss:StyleID="Todo">
        <Cell><Data ss:Type="String">PLUGIN</Data></Cell>
        <Cell><Data ss:Type="String">P5</Data></Cell>
        <Cell><Data ss:Type="String">WhatsApp / Messaging Integration</Data></Cell>
        <Cell><Data ss:Type="String">P5-S2</Data></Cell>
        <Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Sebagai sistem, pesan inbound dapat dibuat jadi activity/ticket draft.</Data></Cell>
        <Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Inbound message masuk ke timeline. Jika tidak bisa match entity, masuk ke inbox “unmatched”.</Data></Cell>
        <Cell><Data ss:Type="String">C6-S2 (webhook endpoints), C7 (opsional jika jadi ticket)</Data></Cell>
        <Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Could Have</Data></Cell>
        <Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Sales:Backlog; Support:Backlog</Data></Cell>
        <Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Todo</Data></Cell>
